# 🌿 POSHAN DRISTI  
### AI-Powered Malnutrition Detection & Monitoring System

---

## 🚀 Overview

**POSHAN DRISTI** is an AI-based healthcare solution designed to **detect, monitor, and prevent malnutrition** in children at an early stage.

It combines **Machine Learning, Computer Vision, and Multi-AI integration** to provide:
- Real-time malnutrition detection  
- Personalized nutrition recommendations  
- Data-driven insights for better healthcare decisions  

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement

Malnutrition is a major issue in India:
- ~35% children are stunted  
- ~19% suffer from wasting  
- 50%+ women & children are anemic  

The main challenge is **lack of early detection and proper monitoring**.

---

## 💡 Our Solution

POSHAN DRISTI solves this by:
- Using **AI models** to detect malnutrition instantly  
- Providing **real-time health analysis**  
- Helping **health workers take faster decisions**  
- Enabling **data-driven government intervention**

---

## 🧠 Features

✅ AI-based Malnutrition Detection (Normal / MAM / SAM)  
✅ Multi-AI Integration (ChatGPT + Claude)  
✅ Real-time Data Monitoring using Firebase  
✅ Personalized Nutrition Recommendations  
✅ Image-based Analysis (Computer Vision)  
✅ Dashboard for tracking child health  
✅ Scalable & cloud-ready system  

---

## ⚙️ Tech Stack

### 🔹 Backend
- Python
- Flask

### 🔹 AI & ML
- Scikit-learn (Random Forest Model)
- OpenCV (Image Processing)
- ChatGPT API (User Interaction)
- Claude API (Detailed Reports)

### 🔹 Database & Cloud
- Firebase Firestore (Realtime Database)
- Firebase Authentication
- Firebase Storage

### 🔹 Frontend
- HTML, CSS, JavaScript

